---
title: Sweet Potato, Black Bean & Feta Tacos with Limey Soured Cream and Lettuce
description: Sweet, smokey, with a good kick of spice, our tacos are bursting with flavour and can be whipped up in as little as 35 minutes. Sweet potato roasted with chipotle paste, cumin and paprika is the perfect meat-free filling, while bold, creamy feta and a dollop of limey sour cream makes each flavour sing.
